[gd_scene load_steps=140 format=3]

; GRASS HUB — Grand Stone Castle of the Penguin Realm (CSG overhaul)
; Scale: player is ~1.5m tall. Castle main body ~60x40m, ~30m tall at spires.
;   4 corner towers ~18m. Terrain pad ~200x200m. Moat around castle.
; Rooms: drawbridge/plaza, gatehouse, grand hall (rib-vaulted), throne room,
;   east wing (mountain warp), west wing (water warp), north wing (snow 3*),
;   south wing (lava 5*), upper landing, sand door (10*), sky door (15*),
;   back bowser gate (25*), crypt basement, courtyard garden, 4 corner towers
;   (each with rooftop secret), attic, 3 hidden key rooms, spiral stair tower.
; Architecture uses CSG: arched windows/doorways, gothic pointed-arch windows,
;   rose window, crenellated battlements, flying buttresses, portcullis.
; Content: 5 bhvBobombBuddy, 4 bhvGoomba (crypt+plaza), 3 bhvCuttlefish,
;   55+ coin_yellow, 8 coin_red, 3 stars, 4 oneup, 1 cap_wing, 1 cap_metal.
; Spawn: Vector3(0, 1.0, 30) on drawbridge approach facing -Z.

